title: BuildReducedGraphVisitor::visit_invoc panic on unwrap
body:
thread 'rustc' panicked at 'called `Option::unwrap()` on a `None` value', ../src/libcore/option.rs:323

I tried to compile the [objc crate](https://github.com/SSheldon/rust-objc), [the `unwrap` failing seems to be here](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/634ecf038d477b8e9aeb815d4cca64939c05781c/src/librustc_resolve/build_reduced_graph.rs#L534)

I expected to see this happen: The compilation working.

Instead, this happened: The compilation making the compiler to crash.
